        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 29 at 6:32PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 631 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 5
miles northwest of Slapout, or 16 miles west of Laverne, moving north
at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Slapout, Gate, and Knowles.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
